               <msContents>
                  <summary>This is one of the most famous books of Mullā Ṣadrā. Considering its comprehensiveness and its influence on the field of Islamic philosophy, the book has acquired a unique position in the recent centuries, to the extent that many works of the succeeding generations of Islamic philosophers were either derived from or inspired by this work. Mullā Ṣadrā has created his book's plot based on the four journeys of the mystics: (1) Journey from the People towards the Truth, (2) Journey towards the Truth from the Truth, (3) Journey from the Truth towards the People, and (4) Journey towards the Truth within the People. The book is compiled in four volumes, as follows: first volume,<foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Fī al-umūr al-ʿāmmah</foreign>; second volume,<foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Fī al-ʿilm al-ṭabīʿī</foreign>; third volume,<foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Fī al-ʿilm al-ilāhī</foreign>; and fourth volume,<foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Fī ʿilm al-nafs min al-mabdaʾ ilá al-maʿād</foreign>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="WadhMinasian_378-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <note type="content-genre">Islamic Philosophy</note>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">al-Asfār al-ʾarbaʿah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar">الاسفار الاربعه</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">al-Ḥikmat al-mutaʿālīyah fī al-asfār al-ʿaqlīyah al-ʾarbaʿah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" type="alt">الحکمه المتعالیه فی الاسفار العقلیه الاربعه</title>
                     <author key="n81035993‏" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/98174078">‎‎‎Ṣadr al-Dīn Shīrāzī, Muḥammad ibn Ibrāhīm, -1641‎صدر الدين الشيرازى، محمد بن ابراهيم، -۱۶۴۱صدر الدين الشيرازى، محمد بن ابراهيم، ۹۷۹-۱۰۵۰ق/۱۵۷۱-۱۶۴۰<addName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="laqab">Mullā Ṣadrā</addName>
                        <addName xml:lang="ar" type="laqab">ملا صدرا</addName>
                        <addName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="kunyah"/>
                        <addName xml:lang="ar" type="kunyah"/>
                        <addName xml:lang="ar" type="khitab"/>
                        <addName xml:lang="ar" type="nisbah"/>
                     </author>
                     <note xml:lang="en"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">بسمله. حمدله. والصلوه والسلام علی خیر خلقه محمد و آله اجمعین. الحمد لله الذی انار بوجوب وجوده الکاینات و اشرق بنور ذاته… و بعد فهذا شروع فی طور آخر من الحکمه و المعرفه و هو تجرید النظر الی ذوات الموجودات…</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">… فهو فی کل شئیی و لیس فی شر و فی کل زمان و لیس فی زمان و کل مکان و لیس فی مکان بل هو کل الاشیاء و لیس هو الاشیاء الحمدلله.</explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="ar">کتبت فی سنه ۱۲۱۱.</colophon>
